    "name": "Torrent & Stream Links",
    "description": "Adds external links on media item pages (movies, series, episodes) to search on configurable torrent and stream indexer sites. If you don't see a Configure button, open the setup page directly: add this path to your Jellyfin server URL — /web/#/configurationpage?name=Torrent%20%26%20Stream%20Links (e.g. https://yourserver:8096/web/#/configurationpage?name=Torrent%20%26%20Stream%20Links).",
    "overview": "External links to torrent and stream search sites; optional Torbox/DMM stream playback. Setup: open in browser — /web/#/configurationpage?name=Torrent%20%26%20Stream%20Links (add your Jellyfin server URL in front). Or call GET /TorrentLinksLibrary/SetupUrl for the full URL.",
